queries.sql: SELECT tc.CONSTRAINT_NAME, tc.TABLE_NAME, kcu.COLUMN_NAME, rc.REFERENCED_TABLE_NAME, kcu.REFERENCED_COLUMN_NAME, rc.DELETE_RULE, rc.UPDATE_RULE, rc.MATCH_OPTION FROM information_schema.table_constraints AS tc INNER JOIN information_schema.referential_constraints AS rc ON tc.constraint_name = rc.constraint_name AND tc.constraint_schema = rc.constraint_schema INNER JOIN information_schema.key_column_usage AS kcu ON tc.constraint_name = kcu.constraint_name AND tc.constraint_schema = kcu.constraint_schema WHERE tc.constraint_type = 'FOREIGN KEY' AND tc.table_schema = 'uretim' AND tc.table_name = 'recipe_ingredients'
